<div class="document">
<p>The system must provide for the following types of user accounts:</p>
<table border="1" class="docutils">
<colgroup>
<col width="50%" />
<col width="50%" />
</colgroup>
<thead valign="bottom">
<tr><th class="head">ACCOUNT TYPE</th>
<th class="head">PERMISSIONS</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody valign="top">
<tr><td>Administrator</td>
<td>Can access any component or area of the system including the accounts of other users.</td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Librarian</td>
<td>Can access the catalog management features of the system.</td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Patron</td>
<td>Can access the general library features, including browsing, searching, check out, check in, reserve, and purchase.</td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Student</td>
<td>Same as a Patron, except students can not access Purchase features.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
